node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Arnar Kristjansson | Iceland on August 08, 2021 tagging @simona_br_photography. May be an image of nature.

node.text:
Beautiful morning at Strútsfoss waterfall in the East,  extremely colorful fall with basalt lava and red and brown sediments. If you're lucky you might catch some reindeers while hiking over there 😎

.
#iceland 
@beyondthelands  @simona_br_photography
_______________

www.beyondthelands.com

node.text:
Set of images when our new volcanic area were in the early stages of the eruption and we had a few craters ongoing all at once . For now Mordor still grows with one powerful crater still going expanding the lavafield closer and closer to the ocean .

.
#iceland 
@beyondthelands  @simona_br_photography
_______________

.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Arnar Kristjansson | Iceland in Iceland with @simona_br_photography. May be an image of nature and ocean.

node.text:
🇮🇸Hæ hó jibbí jey 🇮🇸 gleðilegan þjóðhátíðardag ! 🌧 Today is our Independence day on our beautiful island in the North Atlantic . 

This image summarize the Icelandic mood and spirit for me ,  chaos and storm but in the end there is always light in the end of the tunnel "þetta reddast" 🇮🇸😎

.
#iceland 
@beyondthelands  @simona_br_photography
_______________

www.beyondthelands.com

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Arnar Kristjansson | Iceland on June 04, 2021 tagging @simona_br_photography. May be an image of fire and outdoors.

node.text:
Volcano collection among some phone clips from behind the scenes from the early days April and Mars , now we have one active crater still and if anything it's getting more powerful with no signs of shutting down . Feel this isn't going anywhere anytime soon . 😎

All the volcano images you see here and much more are available in the print store , feel free to check it out on the webpage .

.
#iceland 
@beyondthelands  @simona_br_photography
_______________

www.beyondthelands.com

We have now close too 30 lava images in the print store for those who are intrested 😎🌋
